import React from "react";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

export default function Error404() {
    return ( <
        >
        <
        div id = "errordiv" >
        <
        h1 > Sorry, the page you were looking
        for was not found. < /h1>

        <
        Link to = "/"
        id = "errorlink" >

        <
        button id = "errorbtn" >
        Return to home <
        /button>

        <
        /Link> <
        /div> <
        />
    )
}
